                  </hi>(<hi rend="italic">police-constable L</hi>57.) I took the prisoner, and have the sixpence and the two pieces of the 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. piece—I found nothing on the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400615-name-1332" type="witnessName">
