                        <interp inst="t18400615-name-1332" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>MR. JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of coin to the Royal Mint—these coins are both counterfeit.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I am quite innocent of giving the sixpence, and was not aware of the 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. piece being bad.</p>
